People:
 - Gender
 - Status
  - Hungry
  - Tireness
  - Age
 - Abilities
  - Speed
  - IQ
  - Metabolisme
  - Stamina

Tasks:
 - Captcha
 - Sleeping
 - Eating
 - Reproducing




API:
 - GET  /persons                       -> retrieve status for all persons
 - GET  /person/status/:id             -> retrieve status for person with id
 - GET  /person/task/:id               -> retrieve task for person
 - PUT  /person/settask/:task/:id      -> set task for person with id
 - PUT  /person/settask/:task/:id/:id  -> set task for two persons

